                        <!--  *************************************  <decoDesc>  *********************************  -->
                        <decoDesc>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>"A male figure seated within the panel with various weapons
                                    dispersed around him is shown in a three-quarters view, with his
                                    hands stretched outforwards. He is depicted with a young face
                                    and rich hair; his eyes were damaged, either by weathering or by
                                    iconoclasts. The short light-coloured tunic he is wearing has
                                    long sleeves and embroidered round motifs, one on his upper
                                    right sleeve and two others on the lower part of the tunic; over
                                    it ared mantle, probably a sagum, is held by a fibula. The
                                    weapons around thefigure include an oval shield, a helmet, a
                                    long sword (spatha) and an unidentified round-shaped
                                    object."</ab>
                                <locus>to the right of the text</locus>
                            </decoNote>
